snippet.title: Vapormaze - Trailer
snippet.description:
https://akuno.itch.io/vapormaze
ｖａｐｏｒｍａｚｅ is a roguelike shooter in a vaporwave maze. To escape, you have to manage your ammo, your health and itens, with your Vapetron, while shooting and blowing up bad robots.
